To all Northwest Academy families,

We are officially closed for three weeks as of Monday , March 16th to Friday April 3rd . Enrichment packets for all academic classes will be sent home via the mail on Monday. These are optional and will not be used for anything besides maintaining the academic excellence we are working to achieve and maintain. Additionally, we are providing curbside food to our families Monday to Friday during this time period starting at 9am. We realize the impact this has on our families and while we will miss seeing them within our four walls, we also must take into account the safety of everyone we serve.

Thank you and have a wonderful day
